nodes.text: 5 Ropemaker Road was never used as offices
it suggests his account regarding Ropemaker Road is untrue.
the presence of at least four telephones at the address

Mr. O'Donnell on the face of it a close associate of the first defendant is contacting the claimant there in respect of the very matters raised by the alleged agreement between the claimant and the first defendant very shortly after on the claimant's account that agreement was reached

If there are four telephones at 5 Roper Road and apparently close associates of the defendant are contacting the claimant there in respect of the matters raised by the alleged agreement then this evidence suggests that it is untrue that 5 Ropemaker Road was never used as an office.
